c: 4
v: 78
t: "Wherever you may be, death will overtake you, even if you are in high protected towers. When good fortune happens to them, some [people] say, \"This is from God,\" whereas when harm comes to them, they say, \"This is from you [Prophet].\" Tell them, \"Both come from God.\" What is the matter with these people? They hardly understand what they are told"